casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
COWAN S235296 Supreme Court of California August 24, 2016 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The petition for review is granted. The matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Second Appellate District, Division Six, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of People v. Centeno (2014) 60 Cal.4th 659, 180 Cal.Rptr.3d 649, 338 P.3d 938. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).) Werdegar, J., was absent and did not participate.
